sep.seeter.net.message

Interface Message

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bye, Publish, SeetsReply, SeetsReq, TopicsReply, TopicsReq

    public interface Message
extends java.io.Serializable
    A base interface for messages that can be communicated using ClientChannel with an instance of Server.
